        "message": "docs: marketing brief for ChatGPT 4-week strategic review\n\nUser wants a two-stage workflow:\n  1. Send ctxguard materials to ChatGPT web for strategic analysis + 4-week plan\n  2. User pastes ChatGPT's output back here, I execute\n\nThis file is the complete brief the user will copy-paste into chatgpt.com.\nIt contains:\n  - Project state (repo, release, real data)\n  - SWOT prompt (4 paragraphs, max 200 words each)\n  - 4-week marketing plan (weekday-by-weekday)\n  - Engineering todo list with ROI ranking\n  - 5 immediate actions for tomorrow\n\nThe '附加背景' section is what user pastes back if ChatGPT asks follow-ups.",
